title: Looking For A Pro Duo Q
body:
Hi there I am looking for someone good like i consider myself to be to climb with, current rating is gold 5(highest rank reached was plat 3)
Pref with working mic and a lot of spare time, aiming for diamond... I play all roles, best at jungle/top/adc/mid/supp in that order. Add me in game if you are interested and lets have some fun climbing :)
http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=pycckuu+ak47

replies.body: :/ you were bronze 2 for 6 months in a row, then hit gold 5 in the span of a month, wth

hey dude, we seem very like minded! Ill add you tomorrow. I have a mic and play daily, id love to reach plat/diamond if you are keen to grind. Current silver 2 previously gold 2. I main sup/mid/jg/top/adc in that order.
